---
title: Smoky Tex-Mex Chorizo Meatballs with Scallion-Garlic Rice and Feta
description: In this enticing dinner, chorizo meatballs get tossed in a smoky chipotle sauce that's lightly sweetened with bell peppers and tomatoes. The delicious mixture is heaped on a fragrant mound of scallion-garlic rice, with a sprinkle of feta acting as the perfect topper!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/smoky-tex-mex-chorizo-meatballs-f91f8221.jpg
